#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.basket.appdata.xml:10
msgid "Basket"
msgstr "Basket"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.basket.appdata.xml:11
msgid "Notes and to-dos organizer"
msgstr "Organisator van notities en te-doens"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.basket.appdata.xml:13
msgid ""
"This application provides as many baskets as you wish, and you can drag and "
"drop."
msgstr ""
"Deze toepassing levert zoveel baskets als u wilt en u kunt slepen en "
"loslaten."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.basket.appdata.xml:14
msgid ""
"Objects can be edited, copied, dragged... So, you can arrange them as you "
"want !"
msgstr ""
"Objecten kunnen bewerkt, gekopieerd, versleept worden... U kunt ze dus "
"arrangeren zoals u wilt!"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.basket.appdata.xml:15
msgid "It allows to arrange notes, track to-dos and much more."
msgstr ""
"Het biedt het arrangeren van notities, het volgen van te-doens en veel meer."

